(LOAD_ID, COL_ID, ROW_ID)
LOGGING
TABLESPACE PICTION_MED_1
PCTFREE    0
INITRANS   2
MAXTRANS   255
STORAGE    (
            INITIAL          512K
            NEXT             512K
